    <item>
      <title>印度反对党领袖在保释后猛烈抨击莫迪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/indian-opposition-leader-hits-out-at-modi-after-release-on-bail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度反对派领袖阿尔文德·凯杰里瓦尔表示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的执政党在正在进行的全国选举中正在失去支持，将努力组建下届政府，他在临时保释一天后猛烈抨击了他的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/indian-opposition-leader-hits-out-at-modi-after-release-on-bail</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 11:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据 Axios 报道，特朗普的竞选团队将黑莉视为他的竞选搭档</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/trump-s-campaign-weighs-haley-as-his-running-mate-axios-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axios 周六援引未透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队一直在积极考虑让尼基·黑利成为他的竞选搭档。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/trump-s-campaign-weighs-haley-as-his-running-mate-axios-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 11:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
